    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A seismic design system involving a mechanism which is installed between the ground and the base of a structure thereby reducing the impact of an earthquake.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
